### Keyword Research Integration

**Long-Tail Keywords** (Lower competition, higher intent):
- "how to [specific task]"
- "best [product] for [specific use case]"
- "[topic] for beginners"
- "why [specific question]"

**Question Keywords** (Voice search optimization):
- Who/What/When/Where/Why/How
- "How do I..."
- "What is the best..."
- "Why does..."

**Modifiers** (Add specificity):
- Best, top, guide, review, comparison
- 2025, current year
- Near me, in [location]
- Free, cheap, affordable, premium

